elements.content: Each dish at Kama is crafted in-house—from our signature sauces and spice blends to handcrafted desserts and beverages—ensuring every bite delivers a fresh and distinctive experience.

elements.name: p
elements.content: Kama brings bold, smoky flavor to the forefront by using a traditional Indian tandoor—a charcoal-fired clay oven that seals in natural juices while imparting an irresistible char. From Prime Ribeye to Paneer Tikka, each dish is authentically crafted, richly flavorful, and sure to impress.

elements.name: p
elements.content: Experience a menu where timeless Indian traditions are reimagined with modern creativity — from curried lamb tacos and Prime Ribeye to Kama Lobster Bisque and Tandoori Chilean Seabass.

elements.name: p
elements.content: At Kama, each dish is a vibrant fusion of bold Indian flavors and global influences. Enjoy fresh, scratch-made cuisine at La Grange, Wicker Park or West Loop locations.
